title: North Yorkshire road remains closed after flooding
text:
The A165 Filey Road remains closed in both directions between Prince Of Wales Terrace / Westbourne Grove and B427 Queen Margaret's Road due to flooding through burst water main.
The closure affects traffic travelling between Scarborough and Osgodby.
Last updated Thu 15 Oct 2015 Travel Scarborough Osgodby North Yorkshire
